<p>Reports <code>@Required</code> setter bean properties that are not injected or autowired.</p>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="xml">
&lt;beans&gt;
  &lt;bean class="beans.MyComponent" id="foo"/&gt;
  &lt;!-- reports "Required properties missing: 'port'" --&gt;
&lt;/beans&gt;
</code></pre>
<pre><code lang="java">
public class MyComponent {
   @Required
   public void setPort(int port) // reports "Required property 'port' is not injected"
   {...}
}
</code></pre>
</body>
